<bibRefCitation author="Smith, F." box="[564,715,1557,1583]" pageId="6" pageNumber="157" pagination="357 - 373" refId="ref20215" refString="Smith, F. (1874) A revision of the genera Epicharis, Centris, Eulema, and Euglossa belonging to the family Apidae, section Scopulipedes. Annals and Magazine of Natural History, Series 4, 13, 357 - 373. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222937408680879" type="journal article" year="1874">Smith (1874)</bibRefCitation>
